These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, nigerian
1. the nigerian is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |
| Nationality   | canadian | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, scooter
1. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2  |
| Transport   | taxi | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | horror |

